<p>&nbsp;<br/>
The Olympic Games are a fantastic celebration of what we, humans, can do. They provide us with heroes to admire and goals to aspire to. Despite being a celebration of mostly individual achievement, they take an entire society to organize. This is the true beauty of the games.</p>
<p>&nbsp;<br/>
